posts.post_title: WTB: Last 15 SL'ers for Set (PSA 4.0 - 5.0 graded).
posts.post_content:
Looking for the last 15 Southern Leaguers to complete my T206 set.  Sitting at less than 50 cards needed overall now, so it's getting exciting!
Have knocked off the other SL'ers in PSA 4.0 - 5.0, with many coming from Net54 board members.

No preference for Piedmont vs OM backs.  Main concern is decent centering and eye appeal, with less emphasis on corners.
